cd key problem solution:press windows + re type “regedit” without quotes, and now go to the following location …

HKEY_CURRENT_USER, SOFTWARE, DMD ENTERPEISER, UPRISING 44.
Now double click on a cdkey and zero value data and click OK …
after that just start the game
